articles.title: Texas Supreme Court pauses lower court's order allowing pregnant woman to have an abortion - ABC News

articles.title: Penn President Liz Magill resigns after facing intense controversy; chair of school's board of trustees also steps down - The Philadelphia Inquirer
articles.description: Magill resigned amid growing bipartisan backlash against her Capitol Hill testimony on antisemitism earlier this week and a semester marked by protests and controversy.
